block = """
            # comment
    if test:
        if (lala + hoho) + \\
(foobar + blat) == 5:
            print "hi"
    print "more indent\"
"""
stream = StringIO()
printer = PythonPrinter(stream)
printer.write_indented_block(block)
printer.close()
assert stream.getvalue() == """
            # comment
if test:
    if (lala + hoho) + \\
(foobar + blat) == 5:
        print "hi"
print "more indent"

"""
